  "caption": "Figure 3. .Alphaflexiviridae . Unrooted phylogenetic (distance) tree based on the amino acid sequences of the entire Rep protein of members of the family Alphaflexiviridae . Virus genera are indicated to the right of their respective branches. Numbers on branches indicate percentage of bootstrap support out of 1000 bootstrap replications (when >60%). The scale indicates JTT amino acid distances. Tree produced in ( Tamura et al., 2007 ). This phylogenetic tree and corresponding sequence alignment are available to download from the Resources page .",
